spx.packets.tracks

Class Secondary

  • java.lang.Object
    • spx.packets.tracks.Secondary

  • public class Secondary
extends java.lang.Object
    Secondary information.

    The Secondary structure is contained within the extended track report structure.

    This class is kept in sync with the C++ SPxPacketTrackSecondary structure in "SPxPackets.h".

    See Also:
    Extended
